{"tid":314764,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"想去大板？ 跟住我啦","createTime":"2017-07-09T13:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T00:14:52.000Z","uid":88991,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7dfd1ef338a11861e3a3d2759eaa1dc3f27d3e72","tid":314764,"uid":88991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:30:53.000Z","msg":"係26/7-30/7 會同2老同家姐 去大板<br />\n5日4夜 <br />\n大家對我既行程比啲意見<br />\n<br />\nDay one <br />\n坐早上7點機 &gt;拎埋行李去到難波站大概1330<br />\n我地4晚都住櫻村 係難波後一個站<br />\n食埋lunch&gt;去大板城 影下相<br />\n晚上會反心齋橋 行下同食晚飯<br />\n就早啲反去休息 因為早機佢地都累<br />\n<br />\nDay two<br />\n岀門口&gt;到京都站&gt;嵯峨嵐山站&gt;金閣寺&gt;八坂神社<br />\n晚餐都係反大板食<br />\n<br />\nDay three<br />\n前一日應該幾累 所以唔去奈良住<br />\n岀門口&gt;黑門市場早餐&gt;成個晏就係梅田行街<br />\n加買手信<br />\n晚餐都係附近食<br />\n<br />\nDay four<br />\n岀門口&gt;奈良&gt;大板(掘江)&gt;心齋橋行街晚餐<br />\n<br />\nDay five <br />\n因為我地晚上9點機<br />\n所以有大半日時間玩<br />\n岀門口&gt;難波locker 放低行李&gt;海遊館/動物園&gt;黑門買生果handcarry &gt;機埸<br />\n<br />\n行程大致上係咁 而加係差每日既晚餐<br />\n因為得4餐 所以想每一類搵最好既介紹比屋企人<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"289e89a71a0ed9b9400b10eb764386354821fe48","tid":314764,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:31:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3dd4f802087dc86d9c19646e28d42c131abcf38","tid":314764,"uid":5574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:32:31.000Z","msg":"大板係乜春野.."},{"pid":"ee0995bc8bcf25d0d4327d7704dd4740866f7fe2","tid":314764,"uid":98551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:33:14.000Z","msg":"自由軒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc342b51e5a11a4d5459de2ddd4cc7dfe86ce5a","tid":314764,"uid":5365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:34:37.000Z","msg":"奈良去幾耐？<br />\n<br />\n點解唔係京都食埋？<br />\n唔食宵夜？"},{"pid":"a5f54a3857c02b387ffc7680ff9008f61a180608","tid":314764,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:35:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大板係乜春野..</blockquote><br />\n大塊黑板"},{"pid":"affbdad2c97778acf46f1d6a9d3109181456845c","tid":314764,"uid":88991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:44:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>板你老母</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔鐘意？"},{"pid":"d6a2265acfc75e5be9b77ec0aca66196328a3aef","tid":314764,"uid":88991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:45:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奈良去幾耐？<br />\n<br />\n點解唔係京都食埋？<br />\n唔食宵夜？</blockquote><br />\n去一日呀 京都有晚餐係必食推介？"},{"pid":"e33fd9897a11f7fc50abd33d11ace5c013172bbf","tid":314764,"uid":109050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:47:06.000Z","msg":"跟住你？ 又要人比意見你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f50f77c959e226a39ef5310699380271021459","tid":314764,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:49:26.000Z","msg":"仁淀川我諗要揸車先去到<br />\n定講緊福岡大板井"},{"pid":"35067d9ea0736eebf2146b93d9b419e26e7dcf13","tid":314764,"uid":88991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:55:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仁淀川我諗要揸車先去到<br />\n定講緊福岡大板井</blockquote><br />\n收皮啦 假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf1b481bd99c2d60006e21799483a0e221e245c7","tid":314764,"uid":37675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:56:53.000Z","msg":"你用坂我都冇咁嬲<br />\n<br />\n心諗板你老母咩"},{"pid":"b93b120cc4c959b80a1b585c88b0f738303daea3","tid":314764,"uid":5365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:01:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>奈良去幾耐？<br />\n<br />\n點解唔係京都食埋？<br />\n唔食宵夜？</blockquote><br />\n去一日呀 京都有晚餐係必食推介？</blockquote><br />\n奈良你除咗撚鹿有乜做<br />\n講真 去到兩個鐘就走<br />\n<br />\n京都蛋包飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e464c48a2a4e34